trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup"></xref> objects within a control designer.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup"> </xref> objetos dentro de um controle de designer.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class, and any derived class, defines the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property as a TemplateGroupCollection object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>classe e qualquer classe derivada, define o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>propriedade como um objeto TemplateGroupCollection.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroupCollection property is typically used only by a design host such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: A propriedade TemplateGroupCollection normalmente é usada somente por um host de design como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The collection dynamically increases in size as objects are added.
trans-unit.target: A coleção dinamicamente aumenta à medida que objetos são adicionados.

trans-unit.source: Indexes in this collection are zero-based.
trans-unit.target: Índices nesta coleção são baseadas em zero.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Count%2A> property to determine how many groups are in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Count%2A>propriedade para determinar quantos grupos estão na coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, use the TemplateGroupCollection methods and properties to provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Add%2A> method to add a single group to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Além disso, use as propriedades e métodos TemplateGroupCollection para fornecer a seguinte funcionalidade: - o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Add%2A>para adicionar um único grupo à coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection.Insert%2A> method to add a group at a particular index within the collection.
